00:04:59.833 --> 00:05:01.966
Ya. Dan yang lainnya.

00:05:02.466 --> 00:05:05.400
[.]

00:05:05.400 --> 00:05:08.900
[.]

00:05:09.033 --> 00:05:12.900
[.]

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:22.566
