Kau lucu sekali.

00:06:16.966 --> 00:06:19.166
Tapi kita belum menyelesaikan pembunuhanku.

00:06:19.166 --> 00:06:21.133
Tunggu sebentar, Rex.

00:06:21.833 --> 00:06:23.300
Dolly, ada apa?

00:06:23.300 --> 00:06:24.300
Tak tahu.

00:06:24.324 --> 00:06:27.299
Gini, awalnya aku kesal
mataku digambari kacamata.

00:06:27.300 --> 00:06:29.366
Tapi jujur,
sekarang penglihatanku lebih jelas.

00:06:29.390 --> 00:06:30.465
Dolly, fokus.

00:06:30.466 --> 00:06:31.500
Oh, maaf.

00:06:31.700 --> 00:06:34.166
Itu si kembar Jordan.
Mereka sudah pulang.

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:43.166
Kasihan.
Dia takut ngajak mereka bermain.

00:06:44.100 --> 00:06:45.500
Tidak kali ini.

00:06:50.633 --> 00:06:53.366
Aku tak takut apapun, partner.

00:06:53.390 --> 00:06:54.790
Oh, tidak.

00:07:04.233 --> 00:07:07.766
Ya begitu, Bonnie.
/ Kau pasti bisa.

00:07:21.866 --> 00:07:23.333
Halo.

00:07:38.466 --> 00:07:40.800
Jessie, pernikahan itu membuatku...
/ Shh.

00:07:40.866 --> 00:07:41.766
