00:07:41.790 --> 00:07:43.790
Jadi, bagaimana pernikahannya?

00:07:43.966 --> 00:07:45.633
Siapa pembunuh pengiring
pengantin wanita kali ini?

00:07:45.633 --> 00:07:47.300
Ibu? Ayah?

00:07:47.566 --> 00:07:48.733
Ya, sayang?

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:53.133
Kenapa tak ada yang mau berteman denganku?

00:07:53.700 --> 00:07:54.500
Oh!

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:56.266
Oh, Bonnie,

00:07:56.300 --> 00:07:57.933
