/ Oh, sayang.

00:08:02.766 --> 00:08:04.333
Buzz.

00:08:04.357 --> 00:08:06.357
Kau jadi deputi (wakil) sampai aku kembali.

00:08:06.381 --> 00:08:07.032
Aku? Ya.

00:08:07.033 --> 00:08:10.433
Aku akan cari cara agar si kembar itu
bermain sama Bonnie.

00:08:10.433 --> 00:08:11.533
Ayo, Bullseye.

00:08:29.100 --> 00:08:29.900
Huh?

00:08:30.766 --> 00:08:31.700
Kenapa mereka...

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:35.900
