Tap!

00:09:18.324 --> 00:09:20.324
Tap, tap, tap, tap.

00:09:20.348 --> 00:09:22.348
Hentikan.
/ Tap. Jangan tap itu!

00:09:22.566 --> 00:09:23.866
Dengar saran kami, sayang.

00:09:23.866 --> 00:09:25.633
Carilah laci dan sembunyilah,

00:09:25.633 --> 00:09:27.300
