00:09:29.900 --> 00:09:33.800
Oh, mungkin itu cuma tren sementara.

00:09:33.833 --> 00:09:36.700
Misal kayak, pemutar kaset,
atau Hula-Hoop.

00:09:36.700 --> 00:09:39.300
Kau tak ngerti.
/ Zamannya alat mainan sudah berakhir.

00:09:39.324 --> 00:09:41.324
Berakhir.

00:09:41.348 --> 00:09:43.348
Tap...

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:47.600
Tak percaya kami?
Ayo lihatlah sendiri.

00:09:50.324 --> 00:09:56.024
