00:13:42.100 --> 00:13:42.966
Yeah, sungguh.

00:13:42.966 --> 00:13:44.566
Aku punya pengalaman dengan 3 bocil.

00:13:44.590 --> 00:13:46.365
Bonnie. Sebelum itu, Andy,

00:13:46.366 --> 00:13:49.666
